      "id": "PopularPost355964",
      "post_content": "Sure, it's not great. On the other hand, it's different, and requires a different assortment of counters that ordinary removal. Sometimes, all you need is for your opponent to not attack anyways, AND this is far less likely to be targeted by [naturalize](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=naturalize) than say [paralyze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=paralyze)",
